---
title: Cheese Tortellini, Chicken and Sun-Dried Tomato Pesto with Blistered Tomatoes and Spinach
description: Featuring cheesy tortellini, hearty chicken, creamy sun-dried tomato pesto, baby tomatoes and Parmesan, this dish combines fresh, summery flavours with the wintery comforts of hearty pasta. It brings the best of all seasons!
